Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.65,0:01:00.74,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(960,20)\fax-0.12}I didn't know why we'd received our lives
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.92,0:01:06.35,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(960,20)\fax-0.12}why we all had come into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:12.56,OPEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(960,20)\fax-0.12}I didn't know how to face the one beside
